    "title": "Locked claims trust an arbitrary `tokenLocker` and never verify that a plan was actually created",
    "locations": [
      "onchain_auto/0xbc452fdc8f851d7c5b72e1fe74dfb63bb793d511/contracts/Periphery/ClaimCampaigns.sol:172",
